2.00	CHROMA_Cnife	CHROMA Cnife	CHROMA (also known as CHROMA Cnife) is a kitchen knife-maker based in Demorest, Georgia. The company was found in 1989. CHROMA also sells knife sharpening stones, kitchen shears and other cooking accessories. Well known are Chromas spice cutter range called ProCuTe, a further development of peppermills.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/b/bd/Chroma_type_301.jpg/220px-Chroma_type_301.jpg
